               <msContents>
                  <summary>F<locus target="#1r"/>-38r: Prayer of Incense, ጸሎተ፡ ዕጣን።. Published in Ethiopia, ጸሎተ፡ ዕጣን። (Addis Ababa: Tənśa’e Zä-Guba’e, 1951 E.C.). F<locus target="#38r"/>-45r, and 50r-53v: Introduction to the Miracles of Mary, መቅድመ: ተአምረ: ማርያም: ዘሙዓልቃ:. F<locus target="#45r"/>-49r: Prayer of Repentance for the Love of Money, ሥርዋ ለኃጢአት, including a portion of  Absolution of the Son, Fǝtḥat zä-Wäld. ፍትሐት፡ ዘወልድ፡. <locus target="#18v"/> mentions Our Bishop Abba Salama, አባ ሰላማ (III, 1841-1867). <locus target="#22r"/> mentions ወልደ ማርያም and ወልደ እስራኤል. <locus target="#32r"/> mentions the Egyptian Patriarch, አባ ቄርሎስ, and Ethiopian Bishop, አባ ሰላማ. <locus target="#45r"/> mentions the scribe, ወልደ ማርያም, <locus target="#49r"/> contains a list of names of people who prayed the prayer. Illuminations are added recently over text. </summary>
